703738f-a.title: Brooklyn: Columbia Street - Verona Street
703738f-a.text:
Columbia Street, west side, north of Verona Street. At the
left is seen the American Can Co. on Dwight Street, between
Delevan and Verona Streets.
June 9, 1938.
P. L. Sperr
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
703738f-a.folder: Columbia Street & Verona Street, Brooklyn, NY

705056f-b.title: Brooklyn: Huntington Street - Columbia Street
705056f-b.text:
Huntington Street, north side, east from Columbia Street.
The low building in the center background, seen across the lot, is
Public School No. 27..
June 9, 1938.
P. L. Sperr
NO REPRODUCTIONS
(2)
The same, at a later date. a new addition to the school
is under construetion.
April 9, 1939
P.L.Sperr
NO REPRODUCTIONS
